data.text:
2007

1 hr 28 mins

Drama

NR

Watchlist

Where to Watch

Compassionate, realistic depiction of the HIV crisis in the black community, as seen by an HIV-positive activist and former addict (Queen Latifah) in Brooklyn. Wendell Pierce, Anna Deavere Smith. Co-written by first-time director Nelson George, who based the film on the life of his sister.
